Morgan Freeman to play Mandela in Clint Eastwood's new movie
Despite criticism of the fact that the main roles are played by American actors, the South Africans claim that the new Hollywood Invictus - Undefeated film will expose to the world many things about the country, its struggles and its victories.
History speaks of sport, race relations and Nelson Mandela.
